| ----------: | ------ | --------- | --: | -------: |
|         101 | Ali    | Dubai     |  25 |     2500 |
|         102 | sara   | dubai     |   — |     3200 |
|         102 | sara   | dubai     |   — |     3200 |
|         103 | Ahmed  | Sharjah   |  -5 |     1800 |
|         104 | Fatima | Abu dhabi |  31 |  unknown |
