## 23. Data Leakage During Cleaning

A serious mistake is calculating cleaning statistics using the full dataset before train-test splitting.

Example:

```text
Complete dataset
      |
      v
Calculate overall median
      |
      v
Fill missing values
      |
      v
Split into train and test
```

The test data influenced the training transformation.

This is data leakage.

Safer workflow:

```text
Split data
   |
   +------------------+
   |                  |
   v                  v
Training set       Test set
   |                  |
Calculate median      |
   |                  |
Fill training      Fill test using
values             training median
```

Later, scikit-learn pipelines will help manage this correctly.

